### Creat a user
POST http://localhost:9095/social-media/users
content-type: application/json

{
    "birthDate": {
        "year": 1987,
        "month": 02,
        "day": 06
    },
    "name": "Rimas",
    "mobileNumber": "+94718923456"
}

### Get users
GET http://localhost:9095/social-media/users

### Get a specific user
GET http://localhost:9095/social-media/users/1

### Get posts
GET http://localhost:9095/social-media/users/3/posts

### Create a post
POST http://localhost:9095/social-media/users/3/posts
content-type: application/json

{
    "description": "I want to learn Azure",
    "tags": "azure,cloud,devops",
    "category": "education"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:9095/social-media/users/1

### Sentiment Analysis endpoint
POST http://localhost:9098/text-processing/api/sentiment

{
    "text": "I love this product"
}
